        "text": "3.1.1.1. Wrist extension. There were no significant differences for right wrist flexion/extension between use of a wrist rest and no wrist rest. Left wrist extension was significantly higher without a wrist rest than with a wrist rest (Table 1). There were no significant differences between the right and left hands for wrist extension.",
